item.title: 79. 31 Lessons On My 31st Birthday
item.description: In this episode, Jess shares 31 lessons she has learned throughout her life and business journey. These lessons cover various topics such as spirituality, setting boundaries, embracing change, and prioritizing joy. Jess emphasizes the importance of continuous self-work, honoring gut instincts, and letting go of toxic relationships. She also encourages listeners to capture memories, spend time outside, and build a supportive village... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/jess-angelini/
